 <body region="横下" xml:space="preserve"> 
  <div> 
   <p begin="00:00:01.293" end="00:00:08.300" region="縦右">♪～</p> 
   <p begin="00:01:21.791" end="00:01:28.798" region="縦右">～♪</p> 
   <p begin="00:01:31.759" end="00:01:33.844" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ナレーター）<span style="s3">ジョウトリーグを</span><br /><span style="s3">目指すサトシたちは</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:33.928" end="00:01:36.222" style="s4"><span style="s2">２つ目のジムのある<br />ヒワダタウンの</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:36.305" end="00:01:38.808" style="s4"><span style="s2">すぐそばまで やってきていた</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:40.476" end="00:01:42.394" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピーカー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:42.978" end="00:01:46.357" style="s1"><span style="s2">（タケシ）あ～ ここんとこの<br />日照り続きで</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:46.440" end="00:01:48.567" style="s1"><span style="s2">畑もやられちゃってるなあ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:49.235" end="00:01:51.654" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）暑い… もうダメだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:51.737" end="00:01:53.447" style="s1"><span style="s2">日干しになっちゃうよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:53.531" end="00:01:55.783" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）ここらで<br />ひと休みしましょう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:56.742" end="00:01:57.743" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヒトデマン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:59.453" end="00:02:01.413" style="s1"><span style="s2">みずでっぽうのシャワーをお願い</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:01.497" end="00:02:02.164" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヒトデマン）ヘヤッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:04.834" end="00:02:06.836" style="s1"><span style="s2">（タケシ）うわ～ 生き返る</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:06.919" end="00:02:08.379" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）気持ちい～い</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:08.462" end="00:02:10.214" style="s1"><span style="s2">その手があったか</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:10.297" end="00:02:12.007" style="s1"><span style="s2">よーし 俺もゼニガメで</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:14.009" end="00:02:15.010" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ゼニガメ）ゼニゼニー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:15.094" end="00:02:16.804" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ゼニガメ みずでっぽうだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:16.887" end="00:02:17.596" style="s1"><span style="s2">ゼニーッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:17.680" end="00:02:19.765" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわ～っ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:20.891" end="00:02:23.018" style="s1"><span style="s2">ゼニ… ゼニガー？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:34.697" end="00:02:38.951" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）暑い…<br />体じゅうの水分が蒸発しそう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:39.076" end="00:02:41.745" style="s1"><span style="s2">（コジロウ）水…<br />どこかに 水はないのか？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:41.829" end="00:02:43.455" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）うぐっ うんっ んっ<br />（ムサシ･コジロウ）え？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:43.789" end="00:02:46.166" style="s1"><span style="s2">んがっ んがっ プハーッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:46.250" end="00:02:48.627" style="s1"><span style="s2">あ～ あるじゃないか 水</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:49.044" end="00:02:50.963" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャース あたしにも飲まして</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:51.046" end="00:02:51.797" style="s1"><span style="s2">ほいニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:56.176" end="00:02:57.845" style="s1"><span style="s2">あああ… あれっ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:02:58.095" end="00:03:00.139" style="s1"><span style="s2">何 何 何？ もうないの～？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:00.264" end="00:03:02.850" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャース！<br />俺たちの分まで飲んだな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:02.933" end="00:03:05.060" style="s1"><span style="s2">だって のどが<br />カラカラだったニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:05.644" end="00:03:06.979" style="s1"><span style="s2">（コジロウ）この～<br />（ムサシ）ううう～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:08.814" end="00:03:11.108" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャ？ あそこに井戸が</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:11.358" end="00:03:14.111" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）ごまかそうったって<br />そうはいかないわよっ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:14.194" end="00:03:15.905" style="s1"><span style="s2">（コジロウ）ほんとに井戸があるぞ！<br />（ムサシ）えっ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:18.365" end="00:03:19.825" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロケット<span style="s5"><span style="s6">団</span><span style="s7">だん</span></span>）おお～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:20.284" end="00:03:21.785" style="s1"><span style="s2">井戸～！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:22.202" end="00:03:23.913" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）ニャーが<br />見つけたのニャ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:24.121" end="00:03:26.832" style="s1"><span style="s2">いいわ 見つけた者には<br />権利があるわ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:26.957" end="00:03:28.417" style="s1"><span style="s2">そうだな 権利がある</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:28.542" end="00:03:31.587" style="s1"><span style="s2">残念だけど ポンプを<br />押す権利はニャースに譲る</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:32.171" end="00:03:34.298" style="s1"><span style="s2">持つべきものは 友だちニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:34.381" end="00:03:35.758" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャーは押す人</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:36.091" end="00:03:38.302" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）あたしたち水飲む人<br />（コジロウ）俺たち水飲む人</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:38.385" end="00:03:40.763" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャーは…<br />うん？ なんか変だニャ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:41.055" end="00:03:42.514" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ･コジロウ）<br />いただきま～す</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:43.849" end="00:03:44.850" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:45.309" end="00:03:46.352" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）何これ<br />（コジロウ）なんだこれ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:46.435" end="00:03:47.853" style="s1"><span style="s2">土が出てきたニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:48.354" end="00:03:51.732" style="s1"><span style="s2">そういや ここんとこ雨<br />全然 降ってないからな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:51.815" end="00:03:54.526" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャーがダウジングで<br />水を探すニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:54.735" end="00:03:57.446" style="s1"><span style="s2">こうやって調べると<br />水脈のあるところで</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:57.529" end="00:03:59.823" style="s1"><span style="s2">針金が自分で広がるのニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:00.115" end="00:04:02.451" style="s1"><span style="s2">ダウジングとは<br />いいところに気がついたな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:05.704" end="00:04:07.164" style="s1"><span style="s2">ここ掘れニャンニャーン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:07.498" end="00:04:13.253" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ･コジロウ）<br />水！ 水！ 水！ 水…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:13.462" end="00:04:14.880" style="s1"><span style="s2">お前ら進歩ないニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:15.798" end="00:04:17.841" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）なんですって ニャース</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:18.092" end="00:04:19.760" style="s1"><span style="s2">こういうことも あろうかと</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:19.843" end="00:04:21.845" style="s1"><span style="s2">ちゃんと準備がしてあるのニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:22.846" end="00:04:26.266" style="s1"><span style="s2">なっ なっ 何これ？ うわ～っ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:27.142" end="00:04:30.145" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ･コジロウ）うわ～っ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:32.731" end="00:04:34.942" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）全自動<br />穴掘りロボット</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:35.025" end="00:04:36.986" style="s1"><span style="s2">ディグダ君２号だニャ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:37.361" end="00:04:39.738" style="s1"><span style="s2">わざと私たちを<br />埋めようとしたわね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:39.905" end="00:04:40.823" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:42.116" end="00:04:44.368" style="s1"><span style="s2">それは誤解だニャ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:44.451" end="00:04:46.662" style="s1"><span style="s2">つべこべ言わずに出発進行だ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:46.870" end="00:04:48.706" style="s1"><span style="s2">水を求めてレッツゴー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:48.914" end="00:04:50.165" style="s1"><span style="s2">分かったニャ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:57.965" end="00:05:00.092" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）ニャ ニャッ！<br />水は近いニャ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:00.426" end="00:05:02.052" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロケット団）いい感じ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:11.812" end="00:05:13.814" style="s1"><span style="s2">わあーっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:14.523" end="00:05:17.484" style="s1"><span style="s2">何がどうなってんのよ ニャース</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:17.693" end="00:05:21.155" style="s1"><span style="s2">とりあえず 水のあるとこに<br />着いたらしいニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:23.115" end="00:05:24.074" style="s1"><span style="s2">何ここ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:24.158" end="00:05:25.534" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャンだか暗いニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:25.826" end="00:05:28.704" style="s1"><span style="s2">ひんやりした空気 水は近いぞ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:30.414" end="00:05:31.582" style="s1"><span style="s2">あっ あった～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:31.790" end="00:05:34.918" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロケット団）水 水だ 水だ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:35.127" end="00:05:37.755" style="s1"><span style="s2">（飲む音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:38.172" end="00:05:38.797" style="s1"><span style="s2">プハーッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:38.881" end="00:05:39.923" style="s1"><span style="s2">生き返った～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:40.007" end="00:05:41.592" style="s1"><span style="s2">（コジロウ）ほんと ほんと</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:41.675" end="00:05:42.676" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:43.469" end="00:05:45.637" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）ニャ？ なんかいるニャ<br />（ムサシ）え？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:49.349" end="00:05:50.017" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャニャ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:50.100" end="00:05:51.101" style="s1"><span style="s2">なんなんだ～？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:51.185" end="00:05:52.603" style="s1"><span style="s2">もしかして あたしたち</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:52.770" end="00:05:54.646" style="s1"><span style="s2">怖ーい怪物の巣の ど真ん中に</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:54.730" end="00:05:56.273" style="s1"><span style="s2">落ちちゃったんじゃないの？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:56.356" end="00:05:57.983" style="s1"><span style="s2">そっ そんな～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:59.109" end="00:06:00.402" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヤドン）ヤア～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:00.611" end="00:06:01.403" style="s1"><span style="s2">（コジロウ）ヘ？<br />（ムサシ）は？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:01.487" end="00:06:02.112" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:06.742" end="00:06:09.703" style="s1"><span style="s2">ビックリさせないでよ<br />全部ヤドンじゃない</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:10.120" end="00:06:12.289" style="s1"><span style="s2">なんでこいつら<br />こんなにいるんだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:12.372" end="00:06:13.499" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）見るニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:13.582" end="00:06:14.208" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ･コジロウ）はあ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:14.291" end="00:06:16.001" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャんか看板があるニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:17.252" end="00:06:20.130" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）何 何…<br />ヤドンの井戸？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:20.214" end="00:06:21.340" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）なんニャ それ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:21.423" end="00:06:23.926" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）別名 雨降らしの井戸</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:24.343" end="00:06:26.845" style="s1"><span style="s2">この地方ではヤドンが<br />あくびをすると</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:26.929" end="00:06:30.474" style="s1"><span style="s2">雨が降ると<br />信じられています　だって</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:30.641" end="00:06:32.101" style="s1"><span style="s2">じゃあ ここにいるのは</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:32.184" end="00:06:34.603" style="s1"><span style="s2">特別な雨降らしの<br />ヤドンなのニャ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:35.145" end="00:06:37.272" style="s1"><span style="s2">世はまさに カンカンの日照り</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:37.606" end="00:06:40.567" style="s1"><span style="s2">これって ひょっとして<br />お金もうけのチャンス？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:40.901" end="00:06:43.070" style="s1"><span style="s2">雨が降らなくて<br />困っている人たちに</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:43.153" end="00:06:44.571" style="s1"><span style="s2">きっと売れるニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:44.696" end="00:06:46.198" style="s1"><span style="s2">あたしのヤドンちゃ～ん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:46.281" end="00:06:48.408" style="s1"><span style="s2">よーし 捕まえて売りまくるぞぉ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:49.451" end="00:06:50.577" style="s1"><span style="s2">ちょっと待つニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:50.661" end="00:06:52.246" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャーが見つけたんだニャー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:52.871" end="00:06:56.250" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）さあ 怖くないからね<br />おとなしくしてよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:56.333" end="00:06:57.751" style="s1"><span style="s2">そーっと とっ とっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:57.835" end="00:06:59.002" style="s1"><span style="s2">わあ～っ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:00.254" end="00:07:01.463" style="s1"><span style="s2">捕まえるニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:01.547" end="00:07:02.548" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハニャ ハ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:02.631" end="00:07:03.882" style="s1"><span style="s2">とりゃー うわっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:03.966" end="00:07:04.675" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャーッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:04.758" end="00:07:05.551" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわーっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:07.427" end="00:07:08.679" style="s1"><span style="s2">何するニャ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:08.762" end="00:07:10.180" style="s1"><span style="s2">そっちこそ邪魔するな！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:10.973" end="00:07:14.893" style="s1"><span style="s2">プハーッ ここのヤドンたち<br />なかなかやるわよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:15.310" end="00:07:18.856" style="s1"><span style="s2">こうニャッたら ディグダ君２号の<br />秘密兵器を使うニャ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:19.022" end="00:07:21.692" style="s1"><span style="s2">そんなもんが あるんなら<br />さっさと使えーっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:21.859" end="00:07:23.318" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤアー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:26.822" end="00:07:28.824" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）川も<br />干上がっちゃってるわ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:28.907" end="00:07:31.451" style="s1"><span style="s2">日照りの影響は<br />思ったより ひどいわね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:31.535" end="00:07:32.578" style="s1"><span style="s2">（タケシ）うーん…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:32.703" end="00:07:35.372" style="s1"><span style="s2">おっ やっとヒワダタウンが<br />見えてきたぞ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:35.455" end="00:07:37.416" style="s1"><span style="s2">よーし 早速ジムへ行こうぜ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:37.499" end="00:07:39.001" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）ちょっと待った</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:39.334" end="00:07:41.211" style="s1"><span style="s2">まずは おつかいが先よ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:41.378" end="00:07:43.046" style="s1"><span style="s2">ジム戦が先だよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:43.213" end="00:07:45.257" style="s1"><span style="s2">大木戸博士に頼まれたでしょ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:45.340" end="00:07:46.758" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヒワダタウンのガンテツさんに</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:46.842" end="00:07:48.927" style="s1"><span style="s2">ＧＳボールを届けてくれって</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:49.219" end="00:07:51.054" style="s1"><span style="s2">ジム戦のあとで いいじゃないか</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:51.138" end="00:07:53.348" style="s1"><span style="s2">早く２個目のバッチを<br />ゲットしたいんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:53.432" end="00:07:55.225" style="s1"><span style="s2">きょう できることは<br />あしたに回さない</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:55.309" end="00:07:56.768" style="s1"><span style="s2">約束は大事よ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:57.019" end="00:07:59.062" style="s1"><span style="s2">ジム戦だって大事だよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:59.146" end="00:08:00.063" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ･カスミ）うむむ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:00.147" end="00:08:02.941" style="s1"><span style="s2">（タケシ）でも ジムは閉まってるぞ<br />（サトシ･カスミ）え？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:03.358" end="00:08:07.070" style="s1"><span style="s2">連日の日照りのため<br />給水制限となりましたので</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:07.154" end="00:08:09.656" style="s1"><span style="s2">役所 学校 ポケモンジムは</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:09.740" end="00:08:12.534" style="s1"><span style="s2">当分の間 閉鎖します… だって</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:12.826" end="00:08:13.827" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）がくっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:14.620" end="00:08:16.413" style="s1"><span style="s2">やっぱり このＧＳボールを</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:16.496" end="00:08:19.333" style="s1"><span style="s2">ガンテツさんのところへ<br />持っていくのが先だな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:26.590" end="00:08:28.467" style="s1"><span style="s2">あれって一体 なんなんだろう？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:29.134" end="00:08:32.304" style="s1"><span style="s2">さっきから同じ標識が<br />あちこちに立ってるんだけど？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:33.472" end="00:08:36.725" style="s1"><span style="s2">これ なんだかヤドンの<br />シルエットみたいよね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:36.975" end="00:08:39.603" style="s1"><span style="s2">ん？ 標識だけじゃないぞ 見ろ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:39.686" end="00:08:40.646" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ･カスミ）え？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:40.729" end="00:08:41.563" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ヤドン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:42.439" end="00:08:45.150" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）あ～ あっちにも<br />あっ こっちにも</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:46.568" end="00:08:48.320" style="s1"><span style="s2">この町 ヤドンだらけよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:48.612" end="00:08:49.696" style="s1"><span style="s2">ほんとだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:50.489" end="00:08:52.658" style="s1"><span style="s2">でも なんで<br />こんなにたくさんの…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:52.866" end="00:08:53.659" style="s1"><span style="s2">ん？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:57.287" end="00:08:59.122" style="s1"><span style="s2">あー ごめん ごめん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:59.498" end="00:09:02.584" style="s1"><span style="s2">まさか道の真ん中で<br />寝てるとは思わなかったんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:03.752" end="00:09:04.378" style="s1"><span style="s2">でも ほんと</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:04.461" end="00:09:06.213" style="s1"><span style="s2">どうなってるんだろう この町は</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:06.296" end="00:09:08.090" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）なんか訳がありそうね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:08.173" end="00:09:09.091" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤア～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:10.133" end="00:09:10.926" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤア～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:11.009" end="00:09:11.635" style="s1"><span style="s2">（一同）えっ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:11.969" end="00:09:14.471" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤア～ン ヤア～ン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:14.554" end="00:09:16.181" style="s1"><span style="s2">なんだ？ どうしたんだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:16.306" end="00:09:19.518" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤドンは痛みが伝わるまで<br />時間がかかるんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:19.601" end="00:09:22.396" style="s1"><span style="s2">さっき踏まれた痛みに<br />やっと気づいたのね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:23.355" end="00:09:25.232" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男の子）あいつ<br />ヤドン様をいじめた！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:25.315" end="00:09:26.775" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）えっ ヤドン様を？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:26.858" end="00:09:27.901" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）殴った？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:27.985" end="00:09:28.610" style="s1"><span style="s2">（女性）蹴った？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:28.694" end="00:09:29.319" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）かみついた？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:29.611" end="00:09:31.571" style="s1"><span style="s2">そっ そんなことしてないよ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:31.655" end="00:09:33.907" style="s1"><span style="s2">それに 今のは<br />わざとやったんじゃなくて…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:33.991" end="00:09:35.117" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）おーい どうしたんだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:35.200" end="00:09:36.660" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）こいつが<br />ヤドン様をいじめたんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:36.743" end="00:09:38.662" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）何～？<br />（男性）とんでもねえヤツだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:38.745" end="00:09:40.872" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男の子）逮捕だ 逮捕<br />（男性）警察に突き出せ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:40.956" end="00:09:43.250" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）とっ捕まえろ<br />（男の子）お尻 百たたきだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:43.333" end="00:09:45.752" style="s1"><span style="s2">（市民）そうだ そうだ<br />（市民）やっちまえ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:45.836" end="00:09:47.546" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシたち）うわ～っ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:47.671" end="00:09:49.047" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）どうなってるんだよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:49.131" end="00:09:51.258" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）ちゃんと前見て<br />歩いてないからよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:51.341" end="00:09:52.592" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピカ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:52.676" end="00:09:55.637" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）待て<br />（男性）逃がすな 追え</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:06.648" end="00:10:09.192" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシたち）ハァ ハァ ハァ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:09.484" end="00:10:11.653" style="s1"><span style="s2">このままじゃ<br />すぐに追いつかれるわ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:11.945" end="00:10:14.614" style="s1"><span style="s2">でも この辺りに<br />隠れるところはないぞ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:14.698" end="00:10:15.699" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）おいっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:16.325" end="00:10:17.326" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）何？ あれ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:18.076" end="00:10:18.994" style="s1"><span style="s2">またヤドン？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:19.244" end="00:10:20.495" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）あんたらもこれを</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:20.871" end="00:10:21.580" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤドンが</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:21.663" end="00:10:22.664" style="s1"><span style="s2">しゃべってる</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:22.748" end="00:10:23.665" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピーカッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:23.999" end="00:10:26.668" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）何してんねん<br />ええから はよ着るんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:27.169" end="00:10:27.794" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カスミ）どうする？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:27.878" end="00:10:29.796" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）どっちだ？<br />（男性）あっちへ逃げたぞ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:29.880" end="00:10:31.089" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）捕まえろーっ<br />（サトシ）行こう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:31.798" end="00:10:33.425" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）ハァ… あれ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:33.842" end="00:10:35.218" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）ハア… どこだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:35.385" end="00:10:36.636" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）こっちには いないぞ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:36.720" end="00:10:37.721" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）おかしいな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:37.804" end="00:10:39.556" style="s1"><span style="s2">確かに こっちのほうに<br />逃げたんだけど…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:39.639" end="00:10:41.433" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）どこへ隠れたんだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:41.516" end="00:10:43.393" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）逃げ足の速いヤツらだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:43.477" end="00:10:46.188" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）しょうがない<br />暑いし 出直すとするか</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:46.271" end="00:10:47.397" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）ああ そうだな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:47.731" end="00:10:49.858" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）今度見つけたら<br />ただじゃおかないぞ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:50.150" end="00:10:52.319" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）それにしても暑いな～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:52.652" end="00:10:54.029" style="s1"><span style="s2">（男性）まったくだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:56.782" end="00:10:59.201" style="s1"><span style="s2">ありがとうございます<br />助かりました</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:59.493" end="00:11:00.160" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）この町では</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:00.243" end="00:11:02.788" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤドン様は<br />神様みたいなもんなんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:02.913" end="00:11:04.539" style="s1"><span style="s2">気いつけな あかんで</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:04.706" end="00:11:06.124" style="s1"><span style="s2">どうして神様なんです？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:06.708" end="00:11:10.128" style="s1"><span style="s2">うむ… 昔 昔<br />ちょうど今みたいに</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:10.212" end="00:11:12.381" style="s1"><span style="s2">日照りが続いとるときやった</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:13.006" end="00:11:17.177" style="s1"><span style="s2">あれは そうやな<br />今から400年ほど前のこっちゃ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:18.178" end="00:11:21.306" style="s4"><span style="s2">毎日毎日カンカン照りで<br />畑もかれて</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:21.390" end="00:11:24.142" style="s4"><span style="s2">町は全滅しかかっとったそーや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:25.435" end="00:11:29.314" style="s4"><span style="s2">そんなある日 １匹の<br />ヤドンが現れよったんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:29.523" end="00:11:31.733" style="s4"><span style="s2">ほんでもって そのヤドンが</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:32.734" end="00:11:35.445" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヤドン）フワァ～ ア～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:35.529" end="00:11:38.198" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）…<span style="s3">と</span><br /><span style="s3">大きなあくびをするとや</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:38.740" end="00:11:41.034" style="s4"><span style="s2">どや 一天にわかに かき曇り</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:41.118" end="00:11:45.747" style="s4"><span style="s2">大粒の雨が降り出して<br />町は救われたんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:46.957" end="00:11:49.418" style="s1"><span style="s2">それ以来 町ではヤドン様のことを</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:49.501" end="00:11:52.421" style="s1"><span style="s2">神様みたいに<br />敬っとるちゅうわけや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:52.796" end="00:11:55.424" style="s1"><span style="s2">へえ そんな訳があったのか</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:55.549" end="00:11:56.800" style="s1"><span style="s2">なるほどね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:56.967" end="00:11:59.970" style="s1"><span style="s2">でもおじさんは なぜ<br />ヤドンの着ぐるみを着てるの？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:00.512" end="00:12:02.889" style="s1"><span style="s2">決まっとるがな<br />これはヤドンの井戸におる</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:02.973" end="00:12:05.225" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヤドン様を脅かさんようにやな…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:05.392" end="00:12:06.351" style="s1"><span style="s2">あっ そや！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:06.435" end="00:12:09.187" style="s1"><span style="s2">こんなとこで油売っとる<br />場合やなかったんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:09.479" end="00:12:11.189" style="s1"><span style="s2">ほな 気つけてな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:11.314" end="00:12:11.940" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:12.023" end="00:12:13.066" style="s1"><span style="s2">あー ちょっと</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:13.150" end="00:12:15.277" style="s1"><span style="s2">教えてほしいことが<br />あるんですけど</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:15.360" end="00:12:16.987" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）今 忙しいんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:17.070" end="00:12:19.114" style="s1"><span style="s2">また あとにしたってや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:19.614" end="00:12:21.283" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ･カスミ）あっ ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:26.413" end="00:12:27.998" region="縦右">（みんな）<br />だ～れだ？</p> 
   <p begin="00:12:31.543" end="00:12:32.586" region="縦右">（みんな）ヤドン</p> 
   <p begin="00:12:32.669" end="00:12:33.462" region="縦右">（ヤドン）ヤドン</p> 
   <p begin="00:12:38.216" end="00:12:40.927" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）ハア ハア ハア…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:42.345" end="00:12:44.890" style="s1"><span style="s2">うーん… やっぱり<br />なんか起っとったんや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:47.058" end="00:12:47.684" style="s1"><span style="s2">ああっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:47.767" end="00:12:49.186" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヤドン）ヤ～ア</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:49.269" end="00:12:51.313" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわっ あっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:52.606" end="00:12:54.816" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわ～ いててて…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:31.788" end="00:14:32.622" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわあっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:15:01.985" end="00:15:03.653" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ･コジロウ）<span style="s3">わ～はははっ</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:15:53.370" end="00:15:54.704" style="s1"><span style="s2">（腰の折れる音）<br />（ガンテツ）あたたた…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:16:37.372" end="00:16:38.373" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヘラッ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:16:41.418" end="00:16:42.419" style="s1"><span style="s2">ヘラクロッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:16:44.295" end="00:16:45.880" style="s1"><span style="s2">ウワーッ トオッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:55.192" end="00:12:55.942" style="s1"><span style="s2">こっ これは？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:56.693" end="00:12:58.236" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）<span style="s3">待ーて 待て 待てー</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:58.320" end="00:12:59.446" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）<span style="s3">逃げるなー</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:00.489" end="00:13:01.615" style="s1"><span style="s2">なんちゅう こっちゃ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:01.865" end="00:13:04.159" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）<span style="s3">悪あがきは</span><br /><span style="s3">やめるニャーッ</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:04.743" end="00:13:06.995" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ガンテツ）やめろ やめるんやー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:07.078" end="00:13:08.705" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ニャース）<br /><span style="s3">あそこにもヤドンニャ</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:08.788" end="00:13:12.250" style="s1"><span style="s2">えっ あっ いや…<br />あっ ちっ 違う ウソッ</span></p> 
